Cross‑Engine Dependencies
DAT integrates with but does not own:
PIE — opportunity generation
SIG — signal provenance
SIM — scenario constraints
GGP — execution authorization
FLO — financial outcomes

Completion Criteria
DAT documentation is complete when:
NS‑DAT‑000 → NS‑DAT‑014 exist
Each document maps 1:1 to the GGP template
Execution cannot bypass governance
All outcomes are observable and auditable

Next engine to generate:➡️ FLO — Financial Ledger Orchestrator